#Yoga is Hindu. #Bindi is Hindu. 

Does this mean you must be Hindu to partake in Yoga or wear a Bindi? No. 

Does it mean you have to acknowledge + respect the Hindu roots of these practices? Yes. 

No more whitewashing of our ancient practices.

Here’s something you may or may not know about #yoga; you don’t need a mat, active wear, mat towels, or props. You can get them. They can be helpful. You may enjoy using them. But, all you really need is your interest, commitment & a good teacher. #truthfultuesday #yogapractice
